=== Events === * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7 / {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (1854) - {{ill|Tora no Taihen|ja|寅の大変|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} - {{ill|Ansei Tōkai earthquake|ja|安政東海地震|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Ansei Nankai earthquake|ja|安政南海地震|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}<ref>[https://cir.nii.ac.jp/crid/1390572174727612416 Tsuchi Yasunobu, CiNii] Tsuchi Yasunobu (ed.): "Historical Records of Earthquakes and Tsunamis in Kōchi Prefecture," Disaster Science and Technology Research Materials 57, i-253, 1981-03-20, National Research Institute for Earth Science and Disaster Resilience.</ref>
== Kinoe-tora Months == In years where the last digit of the Western calendar is 3 or 8 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of Mizunoto (癸) or Tsuchinoe (戊)), the first month of the year is a Kinoe-tora month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).
== Kinoe-tora Days == === Selected Days === Kinoe-tora days are the second day of {{ill|Hassō|ja|八専|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (excluding intercalary days). == See Also == * {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
