== Kinoe-tora Months == In years where the last digit of the Western calendar is 3 or 8 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of Mizunoto (癸) or Tsuchinoe (戊)), the first month of the year is a Kinoe-tora month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft}}).
== Kinoe-tora Days == === Selected Days === Kinoe-tora days are the second day of {{ill|Hassō|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (excluding intercalary days). == See Also == * {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
