{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Wood Tiger|kanji=甲寅|romaji=kinoe tora|onyomi=kōin|p=jiǎyín|w=chia-yin|mi=ʈ͡ʂja̠²¹ ȵin²¹|y=gaap6 jan4|j=gaap6 jan4|ci=kaːp̚ jɐn|mc=kæp ŋin|oc-bs=kaːp ŋin|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yang Wood Tiger also known as Kinoe-tora''' (甲寅, also known as '''Kōboku-no-Tora''' or '''Kōin''') is one of the combinations of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 51st combination of the sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Mizunoto-ushi|ja|1=Yin Water Ox|2=ja|癸丑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto-ushi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto-ushi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Ox|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Kinoe-usagi|ja|1=Yin Wood Rabbit|2=ja|乙卯|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe-usagi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoe-usagi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Rabbit|qq=}}. In {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} '''Kinoe''' (甲) represents Yang {{ill|Wood|ja|Wood (木)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=}}, and the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branch|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branch|qq=}} '''Tora''' (寅) also represents Yang Wood, forming a {{ill|Harmonious Combination|ja|五行思想#比和（ひわ）|1=比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|1=比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|qq=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|4=el|5=Ου Σιν|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Harmonious Combination|13=User:Immanuelle/比和|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Harmonious Combination|13=User:Immanuelle/比和|qq=}}.
== Kinoe-tora Years == After the Common Era, a year is a Kinoe-tora year if, when divided by 60, the remainder is 54.
Before the Common Era, a year is a Kinoe-tora year if, when divided by 60, the remainder is 7.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Kinoe-tora Years''' |- ![[1st Millennium BC]]!![[1st Millennium AD]]!![[2nd Millennium AD]]!![[3rd Millennium AD]] |- | *[[967 BC]] *[[907 BC]] *[[847 BC]] *[[787 BC]] *[[727 BC]] *[[667 BC]] *[[607 BC]] *[[547 BC]] *[[487 BC]] *[[427 BC]] *[[367 BC]] *[[307 BC]] *[[247 BC]] *[[187 BC]] *[[127 BC]] *[[67 BC]] *[[7 BC]] | *[[54 AD]] *[[114 AD]] *[[174 AD]] *[[234 AD]] *[[294 AD]] *[[354 AD]] *[[414 AD]] *[[474 AD]] *[[534 AD]] *[[594 AD]] *[[654 AD]] *[[714 AD]] *[[774 AD]] *[[834 AD]] *[[894 AD]] *[[954 AD]] | *[[1014 AD]] *[[1074 AD]] *[[1134 AD]] *[[1194 AD]] *[[1254 AD]] *[[1314 AD]] *[[1374 AD]] *[[1434 AD]] *[[1494 AD]] *[[1554 AD]] *[[1614 AD]] *[[1674 AD]] *[[1734 AD]] *[[1794 AD]] *[[1854 AD]] *[[1914 AD]] *[[1974 AD]] | *[[2034 AD]] *[[2094 AD]] *[[2154 AD]] *[[2214 AD]] *[[2274 AD]] *[[2334 AD]] *[[2394 AD]] *[[2454 AD]] *[[2514 AD]] *[[2574 AD]] *[[2634 AD]] *[[2694 AD]] *[[2754 AD]] *[[2814 AD]] *[[2874 AD]] *[[2934 AD]] *[[2994 AD]] |}
=== Events === * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} 7 / {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 1 (1854) - {{ill|Tora no Taihen|ja|寅の大変|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tora no Taihen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tora no Taihen|qq=}} - {{ill|Ansei Tōkai earthquake|ja|安政東海地震|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei Tōkai earthquake|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei Tōkai earthquake|qq=}}, {{ill|Ansei Nankai earthquake|ja|安政南海地震|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei Nankai earthquake|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei Nankai earthquake|qq=}}<ref>[https://cir.nii.ac.jp/crid/1390572174727612416 Tsuchi Yasunobu, CiNii] Tsuchi Yasunobu (ed.): "Historical Records of Earthquakes and Tsunamis in Kōchi Prefecture," Disaster Science and Technology Research Materials 57, i-253, 1981-03-20, National Research Institute for Earth Science and Disaster Resilience.</ref>
== Kinoe-tora Months == In years where the last digit of the Western calendar is 3 or 8 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} of Mizunoto (癸) or Tsuchinoe (戊)), the first month of the year is a Kinoe-tora month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Risshun|ja|立春|1=Lichun|lt=Risshun|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshun|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Risshun|13=User:Immanuelle/Lichun|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Keichitsu|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichitsu|qq=}}).
== Kinoe-tora Days == === Selected Days === Kinoe-tora days are the second day of {{ill|Hassō|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassō|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassō|qq=}} (excluding intercalary days). == See Also == * {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}} * {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} * {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}}
